  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Demonstrate the ability of muti-detector computed tomography to adequately perform stress
      testing will result in a veritable &quot;one-stop shop&quot; of non-invasive cardiac imaging that is,
      the ability to directly visualize heart arteries with high accuracy and to simultaniously
      determine the hemodynamic significance of any blockages visualized.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
