  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adults &gt;18 years of age

          -  Adults undergoing myocardial perfusion SPECT imaging

          -  Adults with suspected coronary artery disease

        Exclusion Criteria:

